<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to ServiceNest</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e0f4e5; /* Light greenish background */
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #2e8b57; /* Medium sea green text color */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527489377706-5bf97e608852?q=80&w=2759&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .welcome-box {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Slightly transparent white */
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .welcome-box:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.3); /* Light green shadow */
        }

        .welcome-text h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #2e8b57; /* Medium sea green text color */
        }

        .welcome-text p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #3c6d5a; /* Slightly lighter green for text */
        }

        .btn-get-started {
            background-color: #2e8b57; /* Medium sea green */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 15px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-get-started:hover {
            background-color: #3cb371; /* Slightly lighter sea green */
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 20px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .features-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background-color: #fff; /* White background for feature boxes */
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 30%;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .feature-box:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 20px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.2); /* Light green shadow on hover */
        }

        .feature-box h4 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2e8b57; /* Medium sea green text color */
        }

        .feature-box p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #3c6d5a; /* Slightly lighter green for text */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="welcome-box">
        <div class="welcome-text">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Servify!</h1>
            <p class="lead">Connecting you with local services tailored to your needs.</p>
            <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-get-started">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="features-section">
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h4>Find Services Nearby</h4>
                <p>Discover a wide range of service providers and local vendors who offer services to suit your needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h4>Easy to Use</h4>
                <p>Quickly find what you're looking for with our intuitive and user-friendly platform.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h4>Trusted Reviews</h4>
                <p>Read reviews from other customers to make informed decisions and choose the best vendors.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
